OL,6,FA sub-postmaster who lost her Post
OL,7,FOffice branch after being wrongly
OL,8,Faccused of theft during the Horizon
OL,9,Fscandal is preparing to return to her
OL,10,Ffamily business.
OL,12,FRooprit Gill ` known as Roopie ` ran
OL,13,Fthe Wattville Road Post Office in
OL,14,FHandsworth, Birmingham, which had been
OL,15,Fin her family for nearly five decades.
