OL,3,CPost Office scandal victim to return
OL,4,Cto family-run branch
OL,6,FHer father bought the business in 1976
OL,7,Fand then handed it down to her, but
OL,8,Fshe was dismissed after becoming one
OL,9,Fof hundreds of sub-postmasters accused
OL,10,Fof theft or fraud because of the
OL,11,Ffaulty Horizon IT system.
OL,13,FMs Gill told ITV News Central that she
OL,14,Fwants to return to her branch "for
OL,15,F(her) father more than anything else".
OL,17,FShe continued: "My father ran a very
OL,18,Fsuccessful business and unfortunately
OL,19,Fwhen I got dismissed, wrongly accused,
OL,20,FI lost my job at the time.
