OL,3,CPost Office scandal victim to return
OL,4,Cto family-run branch
OL,6,F"I just want to be back in there and
OL,7,Fshow that I didn't do it."
OL,9,FRoopie had been a sub-postmaster for
OL,10,Ffive years when she was suspended. She
OL,11,Fwent to court facing charges of theft
OL,12,Fand false accounting, and was later
OL,13,Fremoved from her role.
OL,15,FHer father has since passed away, and
OL,16,Fnext year marks the 50th anniversary
OL,17,Fof him buying the business.
