OL,6,FNow, she's working daily in the
OL,7,Fconvenience store behind the post
OL,8,Foffice counter, waiting for the final
OL,9,Fstep that will allow her to officially
OL,10,Freturn.
OL,12,F"I've gone through all the interviews
OL,13,Fand everything," she said, before
OL,14,Fadding: "It should all be going
OL,15,Fthrough once I've had training.
OL,16,FHopefully, that'll be in the middle of
OL,17,FAugust."
